**Overview**

This dashboard is designed to deliver a comprehensive overview of server management, emphasizing key metrics related to server performance and configuration.

It presents critical data on operational statuses, showcasing the distribution of servers by their operational state while highlighting the top manufacturers and operating systems in use.

The dashboard also features visualizations that detail server maintenance schedules, usage, support groups, and firewall statuses, enabling efficient monitoring and management of server performance across different companies and environments.
